Class EntityList<T extends Entity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.codename1.rad.models.Entity
        • com.codename1.rad.models.EntityList<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AggregateEntityList

    public class EntityList<T extends Entity>
extends Entity
implements Iterable<T>

    Encapsulates a list of entities. This list is observable, as it will fire EntityList.EntityListEvent events when items are added and removed from this list.
